%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20call%20it%20seed%20to%20shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20about%20as%20local%20as%20a%20business%20can%20get%2C%20but%20we%20still%20operate%20and%20live%20in%20this%20global%20society%20and%20global%20marketplace.%20We%20get%20our%20heating%20fuel%20from%20Canada%2C%20and%20a%20majority%20of%20our%20glass%20comes%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20primary%20manufacturers%20of%20our%20main%20five-ounce%20hot%20sauce%20bottle%3A%20one%20in%20China%20and%20one%20in%20New%20Jersey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20heard%20that%20there%20was%20a%20New%20Jersey%20option%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20fantastic!%20That%20fits%20in%20with%20everything%20we%20do%20in%20terms%20of%20sourcing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20so%20are%20our%20chili%20peppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20buying%20them%2C%20and%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20quality%20was%20really%20awful.%20Part%20of%20the%20issue%20was%20that%20they%20would%20explode%20in%20my%20staff's%20hands.%20They%20were%20not%20tempered%20properly%2C%20so%20when%20we%20would%20fill%20it%20with%20something%20hot%2C%20the%20glass%20would%20explode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%20employee%20fills%20a%20bottle%20with%20hot%20sauce.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae0cfaeb4be2fff9a4874d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221663%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Butterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%20employee%20fills%20a%20bottle%20with%20hot%20sauce.%3Cp%3EButterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20make%20a%20huge%20mess%20and%20the%20entire%20production%20had%20to%20stop%20to%20make%20sure%20there's%20no%20glass%20getting%20in%20the%20product.%20We'd%20have%20to%20throw%20out%20sauce%20that%20was%20nearby%20and%20start%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20was%20that%20really%20frustrating%2C%20but%20these%20US%20bottles%20were%20about%2010%20to%2020%20cents%20more%20expensive%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lot%20when%20you're%20talking%20about%20Chinese%20ones%20that%20cost%20about%2035%20cents%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20use%20the%20bottles%20from%20China%2C%20and%20back%20in%20November%20we%20did%20a%20whole%20truckload%20so%20that%20we%20could%20stock%20up%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20any%20new%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitting%20in%20that%20truckload%20was%20an%20adventure.%20We%20were%20moving%20things%20out%20of%20every%20nook%20and%20cranny%2C%20and%20everybody%20just%20got%20really%20cozy%20with%20all%20the%20glass%20bottles%20for%20a%20little%20while%2C%20until%20we%20got%20through%20most%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20quickly%20became%20clear%20that%20if%20these%20tariffs%20were%20going%20to%20last%20four%20years%2C%20we%20definitely%20can't%20buy%20four%20years'%20worth%20of%20worth%20of%20glass%20because%20there's%20nowhere%20to%20put%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20in%20business%20for%2020%20years%20now%2C%20and%20you%20just%20kind%20of%20take%20your%20lumps%2C%20keep%20going%2C%20and%20figure%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20paying%20about%2035%20cents%20for%20a%20bottle%2C%20and%20that's%20varied%20widely.%20A%2010%25%20tariff%20means%20I%20pay%20about%20three%20to%20four%20cents%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%20employee%20packs%20bottles%20of%20hot%20sauce.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae0d357bb3f854015cc545%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221663%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Butterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%20employee%20packs%20bottles%20of%20hot%20sauce.%3Cp%3EButterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20sound%20like%20a%20lot%20on%20a%20%249%20bottle%20of%20hot%20sauce%2C%20but%20we're%20usually%20buying%20up%20to%20%2430%2C000%20worth%20of%20glass%20at%20a%20time.%20Now%20that%20%2430%2C000%20order%20becomes%20a%20%2433%2C000%20order%20%E2%80%94%20what%20else%20as%20a%20business%20could%20we%20do%20with%20that%20%243%2C000%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20I'm%20most%20apprehensive%20about%20potentially%20higher%20costs%20of%20fuel%20from%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20paying%20between%20%244%2C000%20and%20%246%2C000%20in%20fuel%20costs%20for%20heating%20and%20running%20our%20equipment%2C%20so%20that's%20an%20extra%20%24400%20to%20%24600%20every%20single%20month%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20government%20leaders%20were%20trying%20to%20help%20small%20businesses%20out.%20These%20tariffs%20feel%20like%20the%20opposite%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20tariffs%20as%20a%20whole%20are%20bad.%20I%20think%20they%20just%20need%20to%20have%20a%20reason%20and%20a%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%20employee%20mixes%20a%20batch%20of%20hot%20sauce.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae0d6e6630eb10385c8304%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221663%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Butterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%20employee%20mixes%20a%20batch%20of%20hot%20sauce.%3Cp%3EButterfly%20Bakery%20of%20Vermont%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20committed%20to%20local%20for%20the%20good%20that%20it%20does%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20an%20isolationist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20there%20was%20a%20store%20near%20here%20that%20attempted%20to%20survive%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20and%20they%20were%20hyper-hyperlocal%20%E2%80%94%20literally%20everything%20had%20to%20either%20be%20made%20locally%20or%20grown%20locally%2C%20with%20no%20exceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20meant%20was%20that%20their%20deli%20sandwiches%20had%20no%20mayon