ldren%20-%20has%20revealed%20that%20a%20senior%20Railway%20Police%20Force%20(RPF)%20official%20had%20asked%20the%20station%20manager%20not%20to%20issue%20any%20more%20tickets%20after%20he%20sensed%20that%20the%20crowd%20had%20become%20too%20large%20and%20an%20uncontrollable%20situation%20could%20arise%2C%20but%20thousands%20were%20already%20on%20the%20platforms%20by%20then%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERailway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20has%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20extraordinary%20rush%20at%20the%20station.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20an%20RPF%20investigation%20report%20into%20the%20incident%20found%20that%20four%20trains%20to%20Prayagraj%20were%20scheduled%20to%20leave%20the%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20between%208.15%20pm%20and%2010.10%20pm%20-%20a%20span%20of%20just%20two%20hours%20-%20resulting%20in%20a%20massive%20crowd%20of%20Maha%20Kumbh%20devotees%20descending%20on%20the%20platforms.%20Reports%20had%20said%20that%2C%20on%20average%2C%20nearly%201%2C500%20general%20tickets%20were%20sold%20at%20the%20station%20every%20hour%20and%20many%20more%20were%20purchased%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RPF%20report%20said%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Ganga%20Express%2C%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Varanasi%20via%20Prayagraj%2C%20was%20scheduled%20to%20depart%20from%20platform%20number%2012%20at%208.15%20pm%2C%20the%20Magadh%20Express%20to%20West%20Bengal's%20Islampur%20via%20Prayagraj%20from%20platform%20number%2014%20at%209%20pm%20and%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20from%20the%20same%20platform%20at%2010.10%20pm.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20Shiv%20Ganga%20Express%20left%2C%20thousands%20of%20passengers%20could%20not%20make%20it%20on%20the%20crowded%20train%20and%20that's%20when%20they%20found%20out%20that%20a%20special%20train%20would%20leave%20for%20Prayagraj%20from%20platform%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20sparked%20a%20frenzy%20and%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20the%20big%20mass%20of%20people%20began%20trying%20to%20make%20its%20way%20from%20platform%2012%20to%2016%20to%20board%20the%20special%20train%20using%20foot%20overbridges%20two%20and%20three.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20usual%20rush%2C%20a%20crowd%20of%20people%20was%20already%20heading%20for%20platform%2014%20for%20the%20two%20trains%20to%20Prayagraj%20and%20the%20overflow%20from%20platform%2012%20joined%20this%20throng.%20This%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20led%20to%20the%20stampede.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentions%20that%20when%20the%20crowd%20began%20to%20swell%20to%20a%20point%20that%20the%20situation%20seemed%20to%20be%20headed%20out%20of%20control%2C%20the%20Assistant%20Security%20Commissioner%20of%20the%20RPF%20asked%20the%20station%20manager%20not%20to%20issue%20any%20more%20tickets%2C%20but%20thousands%20were%20already%20on%20the%20platforms%20and%20foot%20overbridges%20by%20then.%20A%20call%20was%20also%20made%20for%20all%20on-duty%20and%20off-duty%20staff%20to%20reach%20the%20platform%20and%20foot%20overbridges%20and%20the%20station%20director%20was%20asked%20to%20order%20the%20special%20train%20to%20Prayagraj%20to%20leave%20as%20soon%20as%20it%20was%20full.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20notes%20a%20statement%20from%20one%20of%20the%20injured%20women%20that%20while%20the%20stampede%20began%20at%209.15%20pm%2C%20the%20first%20call%20to%20the%20fire%20brigade%20was%20made%2040%20minutes%20later%2C%20at%209.55%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuthorities'%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Railway%20Board%20said%20more%20information%20is%20being%20gathered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter%20through%20which%20information%20will%20be%20obtained%20from%20all%20the%20officers%20and%20inspectors%20posted%20at%20the%20station%2C%20after%20which%20the%20committee%20will%20submit%20the%20report%20to%20the%20zonal%20railway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20had%20ruled%20out%20any%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%20stampede%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20station%20and%20emphasised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20extraordinary%20rush%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20conspiracy%20looks%20at%20the%20moment%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20information%20he%20had%20till%20then%20showed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20extraordinary%20rush%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%2C%20he%20also%20dismissed%20reports%20of%20a%20platform%20change%20announcement%20as%20a%20cause%20of%20the%20stampede.%20%26quot%3BThe%20inquiry%20committee%20is%20looking%20into%20it%20deeply%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739864580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7jcaa93o_new-delhi-railway-station-stampede_625x300_16_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-hours-4-trains-mega-crowd-sources-on-what-caused-delhi-stampede-7736533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20probe%20into%20the%20deadly%20stampede%20at%20New%20Delhi%20railway%20station%20on%20Saturday%20has%20revealed%20that%20a%20senior%20Railway%20Police%20Force%20official%20had%20asked%20the%20station%20manager%20not%20to%20issue%20any%20more%20tickets%20after%20he%20sensed%20that%20the%20crowd%20had%20become%20too%20large.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-hours-4-trains-mega-crowd-sources-on-what-caused-delhi-stampede-7736533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Sirens%20Call%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20A%20Radical%20Film%20Combining%20Merfolk%20Mythology%20and%20Political%20Documentary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739864285000%2C