cut%20most%20employees'%20salaries%20in%20favor%20of%20equity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGroq%20recently%20secured%20%241.5%20billion%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia%20to%20expand%20AI%20chip%20delivery%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgroq-nvidia-software-advantage-cuda-moat-challenge-inference-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESemiconductor%20startup%20Groq%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20once%20so%20close%20to%20going%20broke%20that%20the%20CEO%20took%20inspiration%20from%20the%20US's%20fundraising%20during%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjonathan-ross-groq-ai-power-list-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Ross%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20founded%20the%20company%20in%202016%20with%20a%20group%20of%20former%20Google%20engineers%2C%20said%20that%20it%20took%20seven%20years%20to%20find%20a%20product%20that%20would%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20cash%20crunch%20approached%2C%20the%20CEO%20told%20his%20employees%2C%20%26quot%3B'We're%20going%20to%20run%20out%20of%20money.%20We%20need%20you%20to%20trade%20salary%20for%20equity%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20The%20Twenty%20Minute%20VC%20podcast%20uploaded%20on%20Monday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20likened%20the%20ask%20to%20World%20War%20II%20bonds%2C%20through%20which%20governments%20asked%20citizens%20to%20help%20finance%20their%20military%20efforts%20amid%20a%20depressed%20economy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20literally%20took%20pictures%20of%20the%20war%20bonds%20and%20we%20put%20Groq%20Bonds%20on%20it%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bintense%26quot%3B%20decision%20because%20people%20who%20had%20left%20their%20careers%20elsewhere%20and%20had%20families%20were%20banking%20on%20him.%20He%20said%20that%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewere%20worried%20everyone%20would%20leave%20%E2%80%94%20but%2080