.com%2F2025-02%2Fcbvj6cgo_audi-accident-scooter_625x300_18_February_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaitik's%20relative%2C%20Shubham%2C%20said%20he%20suffered%20an%20injury%20on%20his%20leg.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Audi%20car%20was%20coming%20at%20a%20high%20speed%20and%20hit%20the%20scooty...the%20condition%20of%20one%20of%20the%20injured%20is%20serious.%20We%20have%20not%20seen%20Naitik's%20condition%2C%20so%20we%20cannot%20say%20anything%20about%20him.%20He%20has%20an%20injury%20on%20his%20leg.%20Both%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20caught%20by%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20Shubham%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20incident%20took%20place%20hours%20after%20two%20students%20were%20arrested%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshamshabad-orr-donuts-2-students-in-fortuner-bmw-perform-stunts-on-busy-hyderabad-road-arrested-7735442%5C%22%3Eperforming%20stunts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20Fortuner%20and%20a%20BMW%20on%20an%20important%20road%20in%20Hyderabad.%20CCTV%20footage%20showed%20the%20Fortuner%20doing%20donuts%20(going%20around%20in%20circles%20using%20the%20handbrake)%20in%20the%20middle%20lane%20of%20the%20five-lane%20Outer%20Ring%20Road%20while%20a%20BMW%20drives%20to%20the%20side%20after%20doing%20the%20same%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20the%20drivers%20of%20the%20vehicles%20had%20removed%20the%20number%20plates%20to%20avoid%20being%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739855040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ftrpners8_audi-accident_625x300_18_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flodhi-road-jor-bagh-accident-recklessly-driven-audi-rams-into-scooter-in-delhi-bba-student-arrested-7735837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20student%20has%20been%20arrested%20after%20an%20Audi%20convertible%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20him%20rammed%20a%20scooter%20in%20Delhi%2C%20injurin