t%20this%20approach%20would%20bring%20fairness%20and%20prosperity%2C%20urging%20other%20countries%20to%20treat%20US%20goods%20and%20businesses%20impartially.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flevel-playing-field-for-american-workers-trump-outlines-plan-for-reciprocal-tariffs%2Farticleshow%2F118346158.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flevel-playing-field-for-american-workers-trump-outlines-plan-for-reciprocal-tariffs%2Famp_articleshow%2F118346158.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Flevel-playing-field-for-american-workers-trump-outlines-plan-for-reciprocal-tariffs%2Famp_articleshow%2F118346158.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Europe%20Is%20Worried%20Over%20US-Russia%20Talks%20On%20Ukraine%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESceptic%20about%20the%20US%20rush%20to%20strike%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Russia%2C%20European%20leaders%20met%20for%20an%20informal%20summit%20on%20Monday%2C%20where%20they%20reiterated%20their%20continuing%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20vowed%20to%20continue%20their%20joint%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Moscow's%20invasion.%20However%2C%20they%20failed%20to%20provide%20any%20new%20security%20guarantees%20that%20could%20make%20a%20difference%20amid%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20push%20to%20launch%20negotiations%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20approach%20to%20ending%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20left%20its%20European%20allies%20and%20officials%20in%20Kyiv%20worried%20they%20are%20being%20largely%20sidelined%20by%20the%20new%20US%20administration%20as%20Washington%20and%20Moscow%20plan%20direct%20negotiations.%20Their%20fears%20were%20heightened%20by%20a%20rare%20meeting%20expected%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20between%20the%20top%20diplomats%20from%20Russia%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20is%20sending%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20special%20envoy%20Steve%20Witkoff%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20for%20talks%20with%20Russian%20counterparts%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Associated%20Press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20to%20what%20extent%20Ukrainian%20or%20European%20officials%20will%20be%20represented%20in%20discussions%20expected%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Riyadh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20Ukraine%20envoy%2C%20Keith%20Kellogg%2C%20said%20on%20Saturday%20Europe%20would%20not%20have%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table.%20Instead%2C%20Washington%20sent%20a%20questionnaire%20to%20European%20capitals%20to%20ask%20what%20they%20could%20contribute%20to%20security%20guarantees%20for%20Kyiv%2C%20and%20who%20was%20ready%20to%20deploy%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEuropean%20Worries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%20has%20majorly%20relied%20on%20a%20security%20umbrella%20provided%20by%20the%20United%20States%20since%20World%20War%20II.%20But%20with%20Mr%20Trump%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20who%20does%20not%20prioritise%20relations%20either%20with%20European%20partners%20or%20their%20defence%2C%20Europe%20needs%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20united%20front%20on%20security%20spending%20and%20Ukraine's%20future%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20Washington-Moscow%20talks%20over%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20how%20emboldened%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20feels%20by%20them%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20European%20fear%20this%20could%20end%20up%20changing%20their%20continent's%20security%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Putin%20has%20historically%20resented%20the%20spread%20of%20NATO%20eastwards.%20Russian%20neighbours%20-%20the%20tiny%2C%20former%20Soviet%20Baltic%20States%20and%20also%20Poland%20-%20now%20feel%20particularly%20exposed%20amid%20the%20current%20scenario.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20newspaper%20Le%20Monde%20said%20the%20rupture%20between%20Europe%20and%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20added%20that%20Europe%20had%20to%20show%20its%20capacity%20to%20ensure%20its%20own%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEuropean%20blindness%20came%20to%20an%20abrupt%20end%20in%20Munich.%20From%20now%20on%2C%20the%20security%20of%20the%20continent%20depends%20essentially%20on%20the%20Europeans%20themselves%2C%20and%20on%20their%20ability%20to%20maintain%20their%20unity%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalks%20In%20France%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20informal%20summit%20in%20Paris%20among%20European%20leaders%20concluded%20without%20any%20concrete%20announcement%2C%20as%20the%20idea%20of%20deploying%20peacekeeping%20troops%20to%20Ukraine%20remains%20highly%20divisive%2C%20with%20France%20and%20Britain%20pushing%20for%20security%20guarantees%20and%20Germany%20bristling%20at%20suggestions%20troops%20could%20be%20deployed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20meeting%20attended%20by%20representatives%20of%20Germany%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Italy%2C%20Poland%2C%20Spain%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Denmark%2C%20NATO%2C%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%2C%20leaders%20weighed%20measures%20including%20ramping%20up%20defence%20spending%20to%20be%20less%20dependent%20on%20the%20US%2C%20providing%20security%20guarantees%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20and%20sending%20troops%20to%20Ukraine%20as%20peacekeepers%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20talks%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20held%20telephone%20talks%20with%20both%20President%20Trump%20and%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%2C%20he%20said%20early%20Tuesday%2C%20calling%20for%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20and%20credible%20security%20guarantees%26quot%3B%20for%20Ukraine%20so%20that%20a%20peace%20deal%20does%20not%20end%20up%20like%20the%202014%20and%202015%20Minsk%20agreements%20that%20failed%20to%20resolve%20the%20conflict%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zelenskyy%20later%20said%20he%20and%20Mr%20Macron%20shared%20a%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20vision%26quot%3B%20for%20how%20to%20achieve%20peace%2C%20including%20that%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20guarantees%20must%20be%20robust%20and%20reliable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20social%20media%20after%20the%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bprepared%20to%20consider%20committing%20British%20forces%20on%20the%20ground%20alongside%20others%20if%20there%20is%20a%20lasting%20peace%20agreement.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20insisted%20Washington%20had%20to%20be%20involved%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthere%20must%20be%20a%20US%20backstop%20because%20a%20US%20security%20guarantee%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20effectively%20deter%20Russia%20from%20attacking%20Ukraine%20again.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20chief%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20also%20said%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20deserves%20peace%20through%20strength%26quot%3B%20and%20this%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Brespectful%20of%20its%20independence%2C%20sovereignty%2C%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20with%20strong%20security%20guarantees%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReady%20and%20willing%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20how%20NATO%20chief%20Mark%20Rutte%20described%20Europe's%20position%20after%20the%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BThe%20details%20will%20need%20to%20be%20decided%20but%20the%20commitment%20is%20clear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20the%20talks%2C%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%2C%20who%20faces%20an%20election%20on%20Sunday%2C%20said%20that%20any%20debate%20on%20sending%20peacekeepers%20to%20Ukraine%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20premature%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20inappropriate%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20war%20was%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanish%20Prime%20Minister%20Mette%20Frederiksen%20said%20her%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Bopen-minded%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20troops%20but%20warned%20a%20key%20question%20was%20if%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20to%20back%20up%20on%20Europe%26quot%3B%20if%20troops%20were%20sent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20%26quot%3Bthreatening%20all%20Europe%20now%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20added%2C%20warning%20the%20US%20against%20attempts%20to%20agree%20a%20%26quot%3Bfast%26quot%3B%20ceasefire%20that%20would%20give%20Russia%20the%20chance%20to%20%26quot%3Bmobilise%20again%2C%20attack%20Ukraine%20or%20another%20country%20in%20Europe%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS-Russia%20Talks%20In%20Saudi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20US%20and%20Russian%20officials%20will%20reportedly%20meet%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20talks%20will%20be%20the%20highest-level%20in-person%20discussions%20in%20years%20between%20Russian%20and%20American%20officials%20and%20are%20meant%20to%20precede%20a%20meeting%20between%20Mr%20Trump%20and%20Mr%20Putin.%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20set%20off%20for%20Riyadh%20with%20national%20security%20adviser%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20Middle%20East%20envoy%20Steve%20Witkoff%2C%20while%20the%20Kremlin%20said%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20and%20Kremlin%20foreign%20policy%20advisor%20Yuri%20Ushakov%20would%20take%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20fighting%20rages%20on%2C%20with%20Russia%20making%20slow%20but%20steady%20advances%2C%20Lavrov%20ruled%20out%20ceding%20any%20of%20the%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20Ukraine%20it%20now%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%2C%20visiting%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20dismissed%20the%20talks%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20regards%20any%20negotiations%20on%20Ukraine%20without%20Ukraine%20as%20ones%20that%20have%20no%20result%2C%20and%20we%20cannot%20recognise%20...%20any%20agreements%20about%20us%2C%20without%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739853960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ffv7ah0ug_european-nations-meet-_625x300_18_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-europe-is-worried-over-us-russia-talks-on-ukraine-7735744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22European%20leaders%20met%20for%20an%20informal%20summit%20on%20Monday%2C%20where%20they%20reiterated%20their%20continuing%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20vowed%20to%20continue%20their%20joint%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Moscow's%20invasion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-europe-is-worried-over-us-russia-talks-on-ukraine-7735744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%3A%20Sensex%2C%20Nifty%20trade%20flat%3B%20BSE%20Smallcap%20sheds%201%25%3B%20All%20sectors%20except%20IT%20in%20red%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739853554000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-sensex-today-nifty-feb-18-shanmuga-hospital-ipo-allotment-airtel-block-deal-125021800091_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20Market%20LIVE%20Updates%3A%20Benchmark%20equity%20indices%20BSE%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty50%20were%20flat%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20amid%20mixed%20global%20cues%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-sensex-today-nifty-feb-18-shanmuga-hospital-ipo-allotment-airtel-block-deal-125021800091_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Aircraft%20is%20upside%20down%20and%20burning'%3A%20How%20Delta%20plane%20cr