22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Frealme-p3-series-launching-on-feb-18-livestream-details-expected-specs-125021800186_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20the%20launch%2C%20Realme%20has%20unveiled%20several%20details%20about%20the%20P3%20series%20smartphones%2C%20including%20camera%2C%20battery%20and%20display%20specifications%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Frealme-p3-series-launching-on-feb-18-livestream-details-expected-specs-125021800186_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Why%20Modi-Trump%20Meet%20Was%20More%20Productive%20Than%20Expected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20well-timed.%20Rather%20than%20wait%20for%20the%20mercurial%20and%20unpredictable%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20say%20and%20do%20things%20on%20his%20pet%20peeves%2C%20which%20include%20an%20obsession%20with%20tariffs%2C%20Modi%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%20engage%20him%20directly%20on%20exploring%20together%20how%20his%20concerns%20could%20be%20met%E2%80%94and%20India's%20too%E2%80%94in%20a%20constructive%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20pre-emptive%20move%20by%20Modi%2C%20aimed%20at%20setting%20up%20at%20the%20earliest%20the%20tone%20of%20India-US%20bilateral%20ties%20during%20Trump's%20second%20presidency.%20Modi%20has%20gambled%20on%20the%20personal%20chemistry%20that%20he%20had%20established%20with%20Trump%20during%20his%20first%20term%20to%20make%20the%20visit%20and%20not%20let%20uncertainties%20cloud%20the%20existing%20positive%20atmosphere%20surrounding%20India-US%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFriends%20Inside%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20could%20rely%20on%20the%20many%20Indian%20friends%20amongst%20the%20appointees%20to%20the%20second%20Trump%20administration%E2%80%94such%20as%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%2C%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Michael%20Waltz%2C%20and%20the%20director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%2C%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%E2%80%94to%20adequately%20cushion%20the%20ties%20from%20the%20unpredictable%20shocks%20that%20Trump%20could%20potentially%20administer.%20Trump%2C%20supremely%20self-confident%20in%20his%20second%20term%2C%20believes%20that%20he%20has%20the%20measure%20of%20all%20America's%20problems%20and%20is%20determined%20to%20use%20US%20power%20to%20get%20his%20way%20at%20the%20international%20level.%20It%20seems%20that%20he%20will%20listen%20to%20his%20advisors%20only%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20support%20his%20thinking.%20This%20is%20positive%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20such%20as%20his%20desire%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20highly%20negative%20in%20some%20other%20ways%2C%20such%20as%20his%20recipe%20for%20turning%20Gaza%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98Riviera'%2C%20ignoring%20the%20terrible%20human%20cost%20inflicted%20on%20its%202-million-plus%20inhabitants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20an%20early%20Modi%20visit%20and%20a%20personal%20contact%20with%20Trump%20was%20an%20astute%20move.%20It%20is%20apparent%20that%20Trump%20does%20not%20go%20into%20details%2C%20is%20guided%20by%20his%20impressions%20and%20has%20a%20loose%20grasp%20of%20facts%20and%20figures%2C%20as%20was%20evident%20in%20his%20joint%20press%20conference%20with%20Modi%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20of%20the%20US%20having%20a%20%24100%20billion%20trade%20deficit%20with%20India%3B%20the%20actual%20figure%20is%20%2445.6%20billion.%20Similarly%2C%20he%20spoke%20of%20hundreds%20of%20years%20of%20India's%20problems%20with%20Bangladesh%E2%80%94what%20he%20probably%20had%20in%20mind%20must%20be%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20Islamic%20invasions%20that%20resulted%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Remarkable%20Statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20remarkable%20that%20within%20less%20than%20a%20month%20of%20the%20new%20US%20administration%20being%20in%20power%20and%20key%20posts%20in%20the%20State%20Department%20not%20yet%20filled%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20could%20produce%20a%20substantive%20joint%20statement%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Modi's%20visit.%20The%20document%2C%20which%20has%20many%20positive%20features%2C%20gives%20precedence%20to%20US%20priorities%20on%20defence%20and%20trade%2C%20but%20this%20is%20balanced%20by%20what%20India%20seeks%20in%20terms%20of%20continuation%20of%20the%20established%20areas%20of%20cooperation%20in%20technology%2C%20innovation%2C%20space%2C%20mineral%20security%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20White%20House%20readout%20of%20the%20telephonic%20call%20the%20two%20leaders%20had%20had%20earlier%2C%20Trump%20had%20already%20made%20it%20known%20that%20balancing%20trade%20relations%20and%20India%20buying%20more%20defence%20equipment%20from%20the%20US%20were%20his%20priorities.%20Accordingly%2C%20unlike%20in%20previous%20cases%20with%20the%20US%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20other%20countries%2C%20the%20paragraph%20on%20defence%20takes%20prime%20place%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20and%20this%20is%20followed%20by%20trade.%20Expansion%20of%20defence%20sales%20and%20co-production%20is%20envisaged%20to%20strengthen%20interoperability%20(a%20persistent%20US%20demand)%2C%20with%20specific%20mention%20of%20the%20Stryker%20Infantry%20Combat%20Vehicle%20and%20the%20Javelin%20anti-tank%20guided%20missile%2C%20both%20of%20which%20have%20undergone%20trials%20in%20India.%20The%20completion%20of%20six%20additional%20P-8I%20Maritime%20Patrol%20Aircraft%20is%20also%20envisaged.%20The%20US%20seeks%20to%20sell%20the%20F-35%20jet%20fighter%20to%20India.%20Without%20mentioning%20it%20by%20name%2C%20the%20joint%20statement%20refers%20to%20the%20US%20announcing%20a%20review%20of%20its%20policy%20on%20releasing%20fifth-generation%20fighters%20to%20India%20(which%20India%20may%20not%20want%20in%20view%20of%20the%20exorbitant%20acquisition%20and%20maintenance%20costs%20of%20this%20aircraft)%20%2C%20as%20well%20as%20undersea%20systems%20(which%20India%20wants).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'ASIA'%20Project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20notable%20element%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20is%20the%20Autonomous%20Systems%20Industry%20Alliance%20(ASIA)%2C%20a%20new%20initiative%20to%20scale%20industry%20partnerships%20and%20production%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%20This%20might%20suggest%20some%20cooperative%20arrangements%20within%20the%20Quad%20framework.%20Partnerships%20between%20Indian%20and%20US%20companies%20to%20co-produce%20an%20advanced%20AI-enabled%20Unmanned%20Aerial%20System%20and%20co-development%20of%20active%20towed%20array%20systems%20have%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20long%20asked%20for%20a%20review%20of%20US%20export%20controls%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20International%20Traffic%20in%20Arms%20Regulations%20(ITAR)%2C%20which%20would%20include%20in-country%20repair%20and%20an%20overhaul%20of%20US-provided%20defence%20systems.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20decided%20to%20break%20new%20ground%20to%20support%20and%20sustain%20the%20overseas%20deployments%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Indian%20militaries%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20including%20enhanced%20logistics%20and%20intelligence%20sharing%2C%20as%20well%20as%20arrangements%20to%20improve%20force%20mobility%20for%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20cooperation%20engagements%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20Focus%20On%20Cooperation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20%E2%80%98US-India%20COMPACT%20(Catalyzing%20Opportunities%20for%20Military%20Partnership%2C%20Accelerated%20Commerce%20%26amp%3B%20Technology)%20for%20the%2021st%20Century'%E2%80%94to%20drive%20transformative%20change%20across%20key%20pillars%20of%20cooperation.%20To%20further%20advance%20defence%20ties%2C%20this%20year%2C%20a%20new%20ten-year%20framework%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98US-India%20Major%20Defense%20Partnership%20in%20the%2021st%20Century'%20will%20be%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20India%20have%20set%20a%20bold%20new%20goal%20for%20bilateral%20trade%2C'Mission%20500'%2C%20aiming%20to%20more%20than%20double%20total%20bilateral%20trade%20to%20%24500%20billion%20by%202030.%20They%20plan%20to%20negotiate%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20a%20multi-sector%20Bilateral%20Trade%20Agreement%20(BTA)%20by%20fall%20of%202025%2C%20which%20will%20increase%20market%20access%2C%20reduce%20tariff%20and%20non-tariff%20barriers%2C%20and%20deepen%20supply%20chain%20integration.%20India%20has%20got%20the%20US%20to%20welcome%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20its%20recent%20measures%20to%20lower%20tariffs%20on%20US%20products%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20bourbon%2C%20motorcycles%2C%20ICT%20(information%20and%20communication%20technology)%20products%2C%20medical%20devices%20and%20metals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20measures%20to%20enhance%20market%20access%20for%20US%20agricultural%20products%20and%20vice-versa.%20The%20Indian%20side%20also%20got%20the%20US%20to%20welcome%20ongoing%20investments%20by%20Indian%20companies%20worth%20approximately%20%247.35%20billion%2C%20which%20support%20over%203%2C000%20high-quality%20jobs.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20sword%20of%20tariffs%20on%20India%20has%20not%20been%20sheathed%20yet%20as%20Trump%20plans%20to%20announce%20reciprocal%20tariffs%20on%20April%201.%20In%20his%20joint%20press%20conference%2C%20he%20was%20quite%20brutally%20forthright%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20high%20Indian%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Energy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20with%20his%20slogan%20%E2%80%9CDrill%2C%20baby%2C%20Drill%E2%80%9D%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20biggest%20hydrocarbon%20power%2C%20is%20determined%20to%20export%20US%20oil%20and%20gas%20to%20all%20destinations%2C%20including%20to%20India.%20He%20wants%20to%20establish%20the%20US%20as%20a%20leading%20supplier%20of%20crude%20oil%20and%20petroleum%20products%20and%20LNG%20to%20India.%20New%20Delhi%20will%20be%20open%20to%20this%2C%20but%20the%20scope%20will%20depend%20on%20increased%20US%20production%E2%80%94which%20will%20take%20time%E2%80%94the%20price%20factor%2C%20and%20alternative%20sources%20available%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20and%20Trump%20have%20re-committed%20to%20the%20US-India%20Energy%20Security%20Partnership%2C%20including%20in%20civil%20nuclear%20energy.%20Both%20sides%20would%20wish%20to%20pursue%20civilian%20nuclear%20cooperation%2C%20including%20in%20advanced%20small%20modular%20reactors%2C%20which%2C%20it%20is%20recognised%2C%20will%20be%20facilitated%20by%20amendments%20to%20India's%20Atomic%20Energy%20Act%20and%20the%20Civil%20Liability%20for%20Nuclear%20damage%20Act.%20The%20hurdle%20in%20this%20would%20be%20US%20laws%2C%20which%20%C2%A0allow%20only%20construction%20of%20US%20nuclear%20reactors%20and%20not%20technology%20transfer.%20Which%20is%20why%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20while%20mentioning%20large%20scale%20localisation%2C%20only%20mentions%20%E2%80%9Cpossible%20technology%20transfer%E2%80%9D.%20For%20India%2C%20carrying%20forward%20the%20iCET%20project%20developed%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%20on%20cooperation%20in%20emerging%20and%20critical%20technologies%20was%20most%20important.%20This%20project%20has%20been%20re-branded%20as%20US-India%20TRUST%20%E2%80%98Transforming%20the%20Relationship%20Utilising%20Strategic%20Technology'%20initiative.%20As%20a%20central%20pillar%20of%20this%20programme%2C%20the%20U.S.%20and%20Indian%20private%20industry%20will%20develop%20a%20US.-India%20Roadmap%20on%20Accelerating%20AI%20Infrastructure%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20Biden-era%20INDUS-X%20project%20has%20also%20been%20rebranded%20as%20INDUS%20Innovation%2C%20with%20the%20next%20summit%20slated%20for%202025.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20TRUST%20initiative%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20will%20build%20trusted%20and%20resilient%20supply%20chains%2C%20including%20for%20semiconductors%2C%20critical%20minerals%2C%20advanced%20materials%20and%20pharmaceuticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECritical%20Minerals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20US%20will%20accelerate%20collaboration%20in%20research%20and%20development%20and%20promote%20investment%20across%20the%20entire%20critical%20mineral%20value%20chain%2C%20through%20the%20Mineral%20Security%20Partnership%20as%20well%2C%20established%20during%20the%20Biden%20administration.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Mineral%20Recovery%20initiative%2C%20a%20new%20US-India%20programme%20to%20recover%20and%20process%20critical%20minerals%20(including%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20and%20rare%20earths)%20from%20heavy%20industries%20like%20aluminum%2C%20coal%20mining%20and%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202025%20is%20also%20slated%20to%20be%20a%20pioneering%20one%20for%20US-India%20civil%20space%20cooperation%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20a%20NASA-ISRO%20effort%20to%20bring%20the%20first%20Indian%20astronaut%20to%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%2C%20and%20early%20launch%20of%20the%20joint%20%E2%80%98NISAR'%20mission%2C%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%20to%20systematically%20map%20changes%20to%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20using%20dual%20radars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paragraph%20on%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20the%20Quad%20is%20somewhat%20perfunctory.%20The%20joint%20statement%20avoids%20any%20direct%20references%20to%20the%20China%20threat.%20However%2C%20ahead%20of%20hosting%20Trump%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20the%20Quad%20leaders'%20summit%2C%20Modi%20and%20Trump%20will%20activate%20new%20Quad%20initiatives%20on%20shared%20airlift%20capacity%20to%20support%20civilian%20response%20to%20natural%20disasters%20and%2C%20significantly%2C%20maritime%20patrols%20to%20improve%20interoperability.%20In%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20US%20has%20appreciated%20India's%20role%20as%20a%20net%20security%20provider%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20IMEC%20Corridor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20also%20want%20to%20push%20forward%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Corridor%20and%20the%20I2U2%20Group%20within%20the%20next%20six%20months%20and%20will%20announce%20new%20initiatives%20in%202025.%20This%20is%20ambitious%2C%20given%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%20Gaza%20conflict%20on%20Israel's%20position%20in%20the%20Arab%20world.%20The%20intention%20to%20build%20new%20plurilateral%20anchor%20partnerships%20in%20the%20Western%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Indo-Pacific%20in%20defence%2C%20technology%2C%20energy%20and%20critical%20minerals%2C%20which%20Modi%20and%20Trump%20will%20expect%20to%20announce%20by%20fall%20of%202025%2C%20is%20intriguing%20in%20so%20far%20as%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20is%20concerned%2C%20as%20the%20plurilateral%20anchor%20partnership%20already%20exists%20there%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Quad.%20On%20the%20ongoing%20controversy%20in%20the%20US%20about%20H1B%20visas%2C%20India%20has%20highlighted%20in%20the%20joint%20statement%20some%20positive%20aspects%20of%20people-to-people%20ties%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20more%20than%203-lakh-strong%20Indian%20student%20community%20contributes%20over%20%248%20billion%20annually%20to%20the%20US%20economy.%20The%20joint%20statement%20recognises%20that%20the%20talent%20flow%20and%20movement%20of%20students%2C%20researchers%20and%20employees%20has%20mutually%20benefited%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20given%20the%20mood%20in%20the%20US%2C%20both%20leaders%20have%20emphasised%20that%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20world%20into%20a%20global%20workplace%20calls%20for%20putting%20in%20place%20innovative%2C%20mutually%20advantageous%20and%20secure%20mobility%20frameworks.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20leaders%20committed%20to%20streamlining%20avenues%20for%20legal%20mobility%20of%20students%20and%20professionals%2C%20while%20also%20aggressively%20addressing%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20human%20trafficking.%20The%20reference%2C%20in%20this%20context%2C%20to%20other%20elements%20who%20threaten%20public%20and%20diplomatic%20safety%20and%20security%2C%20and%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20both%20nations%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20indirect%20reference%20to%20Khalistani%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20joint%20statement%20contains%20no%20reference%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20or%20that%20in%20Gaza%2C%20though%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20Modi%2C%20in%20the%20joint%20press%20conference%2C%20supported%20Trump's%20moved%20to%20end%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20Modi's%20visit%20has%20been%20productive%20beyond%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Kanwal%20Sibal%20was%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Ambassador%20to%20Turkey%2C%20Egypt%2C%20France%20and%20Russia%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Of%20Mission%20in%20Washington.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739852700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fmhc4gg54_narendra-modi-donald-trump-modi-trump-pti_625x300_15_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-modi-trump-meet-was-productive-beyond-expectations-7735584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rather%20than%20wait%20for%20the%20mercurial%20and%20unpredictable%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20say%20and%20do%20things%20on%20his%20pet%20peeves%2C%20which%20include%20an%20obsession%20with%20tariffs%2C%20Modi%20took%20the%20initiative%20to%20engage%20him%20directly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-modi-trump-me