r%20a%201.5%20hour%20trip%20from%20Minneapolis%2C%20MN.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMiraculously%2C%20only%208%20of%2060%20passengers%20are%20reported%20injured.%20The%20rest%20have%20walked%20off%20unharmed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FP7qbMBj0IQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FP7qbMBj0IQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jordan%20Rhone%20(%40JordanRhone)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJordanRhone%2Fstatus%2F1891587479062315054%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2017%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20later%20told%20CNN%20there%20was%20no%20indication%20of%20anything%20unusual%20before%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hit%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20we%20were%20sideways%2C%20and%20then%20we%20were%20upside%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20told%20the%20television%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20able%20to%20just%20unbuckle%20and%20sort%20of%20fall%20and%20push%20myself%20to%20the%20ground.%20And%20then%20some%20people%20were%20kind%20of%20hanging%20and%20needed%20some%20help%20being%20helped%20down%2C%20and%20others%20were%20able%20to%20get%20down%20on%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChronology%20Of%20The%20Crash%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%2C%20Pearson%20Airport%20said%20it%20was%20dealing%20with%20high%20winds%20and%20frigid%20temperatures%20as%20airlines%20attempted%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20missed%20flights%20after%20a%20weekend%20snowstorm%20dumped%20more%20than%2022%20cm%20(8.6%20inches)%20of%20snow%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delta%20plane%20touched%20down%20in%20Toronto%20at%202%3A13%20p.m.%20(1913%20GMT)%20after%20an%2086-minute%20flight%20and%20came%20to%20rest%20near%20the%20intersection%20of%20Runway%2023%20and%20Runway%2015%2C%20according%20to%20flight%20tracking%20website%20FlightRadar24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aircraft%20is%20upside%20down%20and%20burning%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20emergency%20worker%20told%20the%20air%20traffic%20control%20tower%20after%20a%20controller%20noted%20that%20some%20passengers%20were%20walking%20near%20the%20crashed%20plane%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recording%20of%20the%20incident%20posted%20on%20liveatc.net.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeborah%20Flint%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Toronto%20airport%2C%20attributed%20the%20absence%20of%20fatalities%20in%20part%20to%20the%20work%20of%20first%20responders%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20grateful%20that%20there%20is%20no%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20relatively%20minor%20injuries%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20J.%20McCormick%2C%20associate%20professor%20of%20air%20traffic%20management%20at%20Embry-Riddle%20Aeronautical%20University%2C%20said%20the%20upside-down%20position%20made%20the%20crash%20fairly%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20fact%20that%2080%20people%20survived%20an%20event%20like%20this%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20engineering%20and%20the%20technology%2C%20the%20regulatory%20background%20that%20would%20go%20into%20creating%20a%20system%20where%20somebody%20can%20actually%20survive%20something%20that%20not%20too%20long%20ago%20would%20have%20been%20fatal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAirport%20Delays%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelta%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20said%20a%20CRJ900%20aircraft%20operated%20by%20its%20Endeavor%20Air%20subsidiary%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20single-aircraft%20accident%20with%2076%20passengers%20and%20four%20crew%20members%20on%20board.%20The%2016-year-old%20CRJ900%2C%20made%20by%20Canada's%20Bombardier%20and%20powered%20by%20GE%20Aerospace%20engines%2C%20can%20seat%20up%20to%2090%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2018%20of%20the%20people%20injured%20were%20passengers%20and%20were%20taken%20to%20area%20hospitals%2C%20Delta%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20injured%2C%20two%20were%20airlifted%20to%20trauma%20centres%2C%20and%20a%20child%20was%20transported%20to%20a%20children's%20hospital%2C%20said%20Supervisor%20Lawrence%20Saindon%20of%20Peel%20Regional%20Paramedic%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Toronto%20airport%20was%20shut%20down%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20before%20departures%20and%20arrivals%20resumed.%20This%20led%20to%20ground%20delays%20and%20diversions%20to%20other%20airports%20including%20Montreal-Trudeau%20International%20Airport%2C%20which%20said%20it%20was%20preparing%20to%20receive%20several%20diverted%20flights%20that%20might%20cause%20further%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlint%20said%20on%20Monday%20evening%20there%20would%20be%20some%20operational%20impact%20and%20delays%20at%20Toronto%20Airport%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%20while%20two%20runways%20remained%20closed%20for%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20of%20Canada%20(TSB)%20said%20it%20was%20deploying%20a%20team%20of%20investigators%2C%20and%20the%20U.S.%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20said%20a%20team%20of%20investigators%20would%20assist%20Canada's%20TSB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20Mitsubishi%20Heavy%20Industries%2C%20which%20closed%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20the%20CRJ%20aircraft%20program%20from%20Bombardier%20in%202020%2C%20said%20it%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20would%20fully%20cooperate%20with%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crash%20in%20Canada%20followed%20other%20recent%20crashes%20in%20North%20America.%20An%20Army%20helicopter%20collided%20with%20a%20CRJ-700%20passenger%20jet%20in%20Washington%2C%20killing%2067%20people%2C%20while%20at%20least%20seven%20people%20died%20when%20a%20medical%20transport%20plane%20crashed%20in%20Philadelphia%20and%2010%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20passenger%20plane%20crash%20in%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739849640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fbm