st%20Google%20over%20'Gulf%20of%20America'%20map%20changes%20following%20Trump's%20order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Split%20image%20with%20Mexican%20president%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20on%20teh%20left%20and%20a%20Google%20Earth%20search%20showing%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20right%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3f1966630eb10385cd53f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20has%20threatened%20Google%20with%20legal%20action%20over%20maps%20that%20say%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ELuis%20Barron%2F%20Pixelnews%2FFuture%20Publishing%20and%20Drew%20Angerer%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMexico%20might%20sue%20Google%20over%20the%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20label%20on%20Google%20Maps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20label%20change%20follows%20Trump's%20January%2020%20executive%20order%20to%20rename%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMexico's%20president%20said%20the%20rename%20applies%20only%20to%20areas%20under%20US%20jurisdiction%2C%20not%20the%20whole%20Gulf.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20could%20be%20facing%20a%20lawsuit%20from%20Mexico%20if%20it%20continues%20to%20show%20US-based%20users%20the%20label%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20entire%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20which%20touches%20the%20US%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Cuba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyVJkGqLM5WQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20said%20that%20Mexico%20will%20sue%20Google%20if%20the%20tech%20giant%20does%20not%20change%20the%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20label%20to%20cover%20only%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20body%20of%20water%20under%20US%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20January%2020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20rename%20the%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20pertains%20only%20to%20its%20own%20continental%20shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%2022%20nautical%20miles%2C%20not%20the%20entire%20gulf%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheinbaum%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Google%20is%20also%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20continental%20shelves%20of%20Mexico%20and%20Cuba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mexican%20government%20has%20been%20discussing%20this%20matter%20with%20Google%20since%20January.%20Sheinbaum%20shared%20her%20government's%20response%20to%20Google's%20most%20recent%20letter%20on%20its%20maps%2C%20saying%20that%20under%20no%20circumstances%20will%20Mexico%20accept%20the%20renaming%20of%20any%20geographical%20area%20that%20includes%20its%20national%20territory%20or%20that%20falls%20under%20its%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20reference%20to%20the%20'Gulf%20of%20America'%20initiative%20on%20your%20Google%20Maps%20platform%20must%20be%20exclusively%20limited%20to%20the%20marine%20area%20under%20US%20jurisdiction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%20%26quot%3BAny%20extension%20beyond%20that%20zone%20exceeds%20the%20authority%20of%20any%20national%20government%20or%20private%20entity.%20Should%20that%20be%20the%20case%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Mexico%20will%20take%20the%20appropriate%20legal%20actions%20as%20deemed%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheinbaum%2C%20who%20noted%20last%20week%20that%20a%20civil%20suit%20was%20possible%2C%20said%20Monday%20that%20the%20Mexican%20government%20would%20await%20Google's%20response%20before%20proceeding%20with%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20Google%20but%20has%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20renames%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20as%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af68986630eb10385cac11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20beside%20a%20large%20map%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EROBERTO%20SCHMIDT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%207%2C%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20his%20second%20term%2C%20Trump%20stated%20his%20intention%20to%20rename%20the%20Gulf.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20beautiful%20name%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20appropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Sheinbaum%20sarcastically%20remarked%20that%20North%20America%20should%20be%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparts-us-america-mexicana-mexican-president-says-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAm%C3%A9rica%20Mexicana%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BMexican%20America%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20because%20a%2017th-century%20map%20labeled%20the%20continent%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20to%20officially%20rename%20the%20body%20of%20water%2C%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-maps-changes-gulf-of-mexico-america-name-trump-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Maps%20and%20Apple%20Maps%3C%2Fa%3E%20updated%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico's%20name%20to%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20for%20people%20in%20the%20US.%20For%20users%20based%20outside%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Mexico%2C%20the%20body%20of%20water%20shows%20up%20as%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico%20(Gulf%20of%20America).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichigan%20State%20University%20political%20science%20professor%20Matthew%20Zierler%2C%20who%20studies%20foreign%20policy%20and%20international%20law%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20countries%20don't%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-renaming-gulf-mexico-google-implications-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erename%20an%20international%20body%20of%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRenaming%20Denali%20to%20McKinley%20is%20within%20the%20United%20States'%20purview%2C%20but%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20is%20a%20different%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Sheinbaum%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20Google%20pushing%20back%20against%20the%20naming%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20company%20responded%20with%20a%20letter%2C%20which%20Sheinbaum%20read%20aloud%20in%20the%20Monday%20press%20conference.%20The%20letter%20said%20that%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bconsistent%20policy%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bconsult%20multiple%20authoritative%20sources%20to%20provide%20the%20most%20up-to-date%20and%20accurate%20representation%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Google%20letter%20said%20that%20the%20change%20from%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20for%20US-based%20users%20was%20made%20to%20reflect%20the%20update%20by%20the%20US%20Geographic%20Names%20Information%20System%20(GNIS).%20The%20letter%20also%20stated%20that%20Google%20Maps%20users%20in%20Mexico%20will%20continue%20to%20see%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico%26quot%3B%20while%20people%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world%20will%20be%20shown%20both%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheinbaum%20did%20not%20say%20whether%20Mexico