ost%20competitor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrontier-first-class-seats-premium-customers-low-cost-airlines-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrontier%20Airlines%20has%20similarly%20made%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20adding%20a%20new%20business-class-like%20cabin%20with%20a%20blocked%20middle%20seat%20to%20lure%20in%20more%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20Southwest%20CEO%20Bob%20Jordan's%20full%20message%20to%20employees%20on%20Monday%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ESouthwest%20Team%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20at%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20as%20we%20carry%20out%20our%20three-year%20business%20plan%20to%20transform%20Southwest%20Airlines.%20Our%20transformational%20plan%20is%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20comprehensive%20in%20our%2053-year%20history%2C%20and%20it%20focuses%20on%20three%20simple%20but%20powerful%20objectives.%20First%2C%20boost%20revenues%20and%20loyalty%20by%20offering%20our%20Customers%20the%20experience%20they%20want%3B%20second%2C%20maximize%20efficiencies%20and%20minimize%20costs%3B%20and%20third%2C%20make%20the%20most%20of%20our%20investments.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20we%20continue%20to%20work%20together%20to%20transform%20our%20Company%2C%20an%20area%20of%20intense%20focus%20will%20be%20maximizing%20efficiencies%20and%20minimizing%20costs.%20We%20must%20ensure%20we%20fund%20the%20right%20work%2C%20reduce%20duplicative%20efforts%2C%20and%20have%20a%20lean%20organizational%20structure%20that%20drives%20clarity%2C%20pace%2C%20and%20urgency.%20Improving%20how%20we%20work%20together%20and%20how%20we%20get%20work%20done%20has%20a%20tremendous%20impact%20on%20our%20efficiency%20as%20a%20Company%20and%20how%20we%20deliver%20against%20our%20plan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20have%20made%20the%20very%20tough%20decision%20to%20move%20forward%20with%20a%20reduction%20in%20our%20workforce%2C%20focused%20almost%20entirely%20on%20Corporate%20and%20Leadership%20positions.%20This%20reduction%20affects%20approximately%201%2C750%20Employee%20roles%2C%20or%2015%25%20of%20Corporate%20positions.%20Separations%20do%20not%20begin%20until%20late%20April.%20Until%20then%2C%20most%20Employees%20who%20are%20notified%20of%20their%20displacement%20will%20not%20work%20but%20will%20continue%20to%20receive%20their%20salary%2C%20benefits%2C%20and%20bonus%2C%20if%20eligible.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20very%20difficult%20and%20monumental%20shift%2C%20and%20I%20arrived%20at%20this%20decision%20after%20careful%20and%20thorough%20reflection%2C%20knowing%20how%20hard%20it%20will%20be%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20Cohearts%20who%20have%20been%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20our%20Culture%20and%20our%20accomplishments.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20dedicated%20to%20operating%20safely%20and%20reliably%20for%20our%20Customers%20every%20single%20day.%20The%20fundamental%20objective%20of%20Leadership%20and%20Noncontract%20roles%20is%20to%20support%20our%20Frontline%20Employees%20as%20efficiently%20and%20effectively%20as%20possible.%20With%20the%20best%20intentions%2C%20the%20growth%20of%20our%20Leadership%20and%20Noncontract%20functions%20have%20outpaced%20our%20operation's%20growth%20for%20many%20years.%20Now%2C%20this%20group%20must%20become%20more%20lean%2C%20efficient%2C%20and%20agile%20to%20better%20serve%20our%20Frontline%20Employees%20in%20our%20shared%20mission%20of%20serving%20our%20Customers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20to%20Expect%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20will%20be%20hard%2C%20and%20we%20will%20treat%20our%20People%20with%20the%20care%20and%20respect%20they%20have%20earned%20and%20they%20deserve.%20Impacted%20Employees%20will%20receive%20severance%20and%20will%20be%20offered%20resources%20to%20provide%20an%20opportunity%20to%20ask%20questions%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20future%2C%20like%20sessions%20with%20Human%20Resource%20Business%20Partners%2C%20a%20dedicated%20Offboarding%20Support%20Team%2C%20and%20outplacement%20services.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EMoving%20Forward%20Together%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20was%20an%20extremely%20difficult%20decision%20to%20make%20because%20of%20its%20impact%20on%20our%20People%E2%80%94both%20those%20who%20will%20be%20directly%20impacted%20and%20those%20who%20will%20remain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EChanging%20how%20we%20work%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20becoming%20a%20more%20agile%20Company%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20a%20journey.%20We%20are%20building%20a%20leaner%20organization%20with%20increased%20clarity%20regarding%20what%20is%20most%20important%2C%20quicker%20decision%20making%2C%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20getting%20the%20right%20things%20done%20with%20urgency%E2%80%94not%20unlike%20our%20entrepreneurial%20founding%20spirit%20of%20the%201970s.%20As%20we%20focus%20on%20delivering%20on%20our%20plan%2C%20our%20future%20will%20be%20built%20upon%20the%20actions%20we%20take%20today%20to%20ensure%20an%20even%20brighter%20future.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20one%20of%20the%20Southwest%20employees%20who%20was%20laid%20off%3F%20If%20so%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20Business%20Insider%20Senior%20Aviation%20Reporter%20Taylor%20Rains%20on%20a%20non-work%20device%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atrains%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etrains%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouthwest-airlines-memo-layoff-workforce-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739835977000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider