er%20solution%20that%20oftentimes%20includes%20sugar%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0will%20help%20keep%20it%20moist.%20This%20technique%20works%20with%20both%20whole%20fish%20and%20fillets%2C%20and%20Falsini%20recommends%20trying%20it%20with%20halibut%20or%20snapper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20mix%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20sugar%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20salt%20%E2%80%94%20normally%20it's%20two%20parts%20salt%2C%20one%20part%20sugar%20%E2%80%94%20with%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20Falsini%20said.%20%26quot%3BBrine%20the%20fish%20for%20about%2030%20minutes%20before%20you%20cook%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20make%20sure%20to%20dry%20the%20fish%20well%20before%20you%20start%20cooking.%20A%20wet%20fish%20will%20stick%20right%20to%20the%20pan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a690037-4ac4-4059-b356-8c7d00adaa71%5C%22%3ERoast%20your%20fish%20with%20potatoes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221433%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roasted%20fish%20on%20a%20bed%20of%20potatoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3b8d67bb3f854015d1566%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221075%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFalsini%20recommends%20roasting%20your%20fish%20in%20the%20oven%20with%20potatoes%20for%20a%20perfect%20seafood%20dish.%3Cp%3EDeepblue4you%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFalsini%20believes%20the%20best%20way%20to%20cook%20fish%20is%20by%20roasting%20it%20in%20the%20oven%20alongside%20some%20delicious%20potatoes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recommends%20blanching%20the%20potatoes%20first%2C%20briefly%20boiling%20the%20spuds%20and%20then%20cooling%20them%20in%20ice%20water.%20Then%20season%20the%20potatoes%20with%20garlic%2C%20extra-virgin%20olive%20oil%2C%20lemon%20juice%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20rosemary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20like%20to%20put%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20paprika%20on%20them%20for%20the%20smokiness%20and%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20Falsini%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20place%20the%20fish%20and%20potatoes%20in%20a%20pan%20and%20add%20lemon%20slices%2C%20crushed%20garlic%2C%20and%20parsley.%20Season%20the%20fish%20with%20salt%20and%20extra-virgin%20olive%20oil%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFalsini%20recommends%20cooking%20the%20fish%20at%20350%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20The%20dish%20should%20be%20ready%20in%2045%20to%2050%20minutes%20if%20you're%20cooking%20about%20three%20pounds%20of%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20check%20if%20your%20whole%20fish%20is%20ready%2C%20Falsini%20recommends%20pulling%20on%20the%20spine%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20fish.%20If%20the%20spine%20comes%20off%2C%20the%20fish%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20just%20remove%20the%20flesh%20with%20a%20spoon%20and%20finish%20with%20some%20more%20olive%20oil%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20fresh%20lemon%20juice.%20Dinner%20is%20served!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-best-fish-at-home-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739833722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3b9506630eb10385cd39d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-best-fish-at-home-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michelin-starred%20chef%20Massimo%20Falsini%20specializes%20in%20seafood%20dishes%20at%20Caruso's%2C%20the%20restaurant%20at%20Rosewood%20Miramar%20Beach%20resort%20in%20Santa%20Barbara.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22akonstantinides%40businessinsider.com%20(Anneta%20Konstantinides)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-best-fish-at-home-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Deadly%20storm%20hits%20south-eastern%20US%20and%20Canada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739832689000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F22d8%2Flive%2F4dfc7b